Two tutorial codes useful for learning about HPX-5. The text of the tutorials
can be found at https://hpx.crest.iu.edu/tutorials.

Advection1D:
  A series of five codes building toward a solution of the one-dimensional 
  advection equation.

1dtree:
  A simple one-dimensional tree code for computing the potential for each 
  point mass in a collection of point masses due to the other masses.

For more details please see the README file in each subdirectory.

